defaultNGO Monitor
default (
defaultwww.ngo-monitor.org
default), a Jerusalem-based research organization,
default provides information and analysis, promotes accountability, and supports discussion on the reports and activities of NGOs (non-governmental organizations) claiming to advance human rights and humanitarian agendas. 
defaultSince 2002, NGO Monitor has conducted dozens of detailed and systematic research studies on the issues of NGO funding, transparency, accountability, international law, human rights, humanitarian aid, and the laws of armed conflict.
