defaultan important venue for promoting this 
defaultlawfare
default s
defaulttrategy.  On several occasions, anti-Israel NGOs have sought to 
defaultinterfere with UK foreign policy and diplomatic relations
default by attempting to secure 
defaultex parte
default 
defaultarrest warrants against Israeli officials travelling to the UK for high-level government meetings and charity events.  These same NGOs have filed civil lawsuits (all subsequently dismissed) against British ministries to block economic relations between the UK and Israel. In 2011, the British Parliament amended the 
defaultPolice Reform and Social Responsibility Bill 2010-11
default,
default to prevent further abuse and exploitation of its judicial system by these organizations.
default 
default15.
default&#xa0; 
